eks or more because they&rsquo;re ill or disabled and you won&rsquo;t be regularly spending money on them</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Your child&rsquo;s going abroad</h2>\n\n<p>Tell the Child Benefit Office straight away if your child is due to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>leave the UK permanently or they&rsquo;re likely to be away for more than 52 weeks</li>\n  <li>leave the UK temporarily for more than 12 weeks </li>\n  <li>leave England, Scotland or Wales to go to Northern Ireland permanently</li>\n  <li>leave Northern Ireland to go to England, Scotland or Wales permanently</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Other changes</h2>\n\n<p>Tell the Child Benefit Office straight away if your child:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>changes their name</li>\n  <li>starts getting benefits in their own right</li>\n  <li>marries, forms a civil partnership or starts to live with a partner</li>\n  <li>is expected to be held in legal custody for more than 8 weeks</li>\n  <li>goes missing</li>\n  <li>is looked after by a local authority (in Northern Ireland, a Health and Social Services Board or Trust), a voluntary organisation, or held in secure or non-secure accommodation</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>How to report changes</h2>\n\n<p>You can do this:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/childbenefit/change-circs.htm\" title=\"Report a change of circumstances online\">online</a></li>\n  <li>by calling or writing to the Child Benefit Office</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Child Benefit Helpline</strong> <br />\n<strong>Telephone:</strong> 08453 021 444<br />\n<strong>Textphone:</strong> 08453 021 474 <br />\nMonday to Friday, 8am to 8pm<br />\nSaturday, 8am to 4pm <br />\nClosed Christmas Day, Boxing Day, and New Year’s Day</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\nChild Benefit Office\n<br />PO Box 1\n<br />Newcastle Upon Tyne\n<br />NE88 1AA\n<br />\n</p></div></div>\n\n","alternative_title":""},"tags":[{"title":"Child Benefit","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/t